member.name: T:B2R2.FrontEnd.BinLifter.ARM64.Register
member.summary:
ARMv8 registers. Below is how we encode register as a 20-bit integer.
19 18 17 16 15 ... 00 (bit position) +----------+----------------------+ | Kind | Register ID. | +----------+----------------------+
# Kind (19 - 16) - 0000 : General purpose registers. - 0001 : SIMD registers. - 0010 : VFP registers. - 0011 : Co-processor registers. - 0100 : Control flags. - 0101 : Control register.
